}

{
  "headline": "<h2>Autoplay Feature</h2>",
  "content": "<p>Alright, let's talk about something that will make all of us lazy. Fetching Fruits has an Autoplay feature that is perfect for those moments when you just want to sit back, relax and watch the reels go round and round. It's like having a personal slot machine assistant. </p><p>With Autoplay, players can choose to have anywhere from 10 to 100 automatic spins, while setting a win or loss limit. So, if you're feeling lucky, set the limit and let the game do the rest. And if you're not feeling so lucky, well... at least you won't be able to blame yourself for losing all your cash.</p><p>Overall, the Autoplay feature in Fetching Fruits is impressive. It's almost as if the designers knew that we wanted an excuse to just sit back and do nothing while still having a chance to win big. So, if you're feeling lazy or just want to take a break, try out the Autoplay feature and let the game do the work for you.</p>"
